'''Taiwan''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are only the capital, Taipei.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Taiwan; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Switzerland]], [[Thailand]], [[United Arab Emirates]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was later added to Android versions on September 21, 2019.

